ours of the poisoning, do the following:\n<ol>\n<li>open the package, and add to water or non-caffeinated soft drink<\/li>\n<li>drink all of this as soon as possible<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<\/li>\n<li>Go to hospital.<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>50g of activated charcoal within 2h of a poisoning is the first line treatment for poisoning by mouth, as is often encountered in overdoses. This package contains 55g of charcoal, ensuring at least 50g is given. This should not be used for poisoning with petroleum distillates, corrosive substances, alcohols, malathion, cyanides and metal salts including [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"featured_media":8621,"template":"","meta":[],"product_cat":[35],"product_tag":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/queercare.network\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product\/8602"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/queercare.network\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/queercare.network\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/product"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/queercare.network\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/8621"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/queercare.network\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=8602"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"product_cat","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/queercare.network\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product_cat?post=8602"},{"taxonomy":"product_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/queercare.network\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product_tag?post=8602"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}